						<summary>

						<p>This is damaged and incomplete and dated the <hi rend="bold">4th year</hi> of the Chālukya king <hi rend="bold">Jagadēkamalladēva (II),</hi> cyclic year <hi rend="bold">Durmati, Bhādrapada, śu. 6, Ādityavāra</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">A.D. 1141 August 9, Saturday,</hi> not Sunday. It seems to record the gift of some land for a feeding house.</p>						

